What does the following policy for Amazon EC2 do?


```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": {
    "Effect": "Deny",
    "Action": "*",
    "Resource": "*",
    "Condition": {
      "NotIpAddress": {
        "aws:SourceIp": [
          "192.0.2.0/24",
          "203.0.113.0/24"
        ]
      },
      "Bool": {"aws:ViaAWSService": "false"}
    }
  }
}
```
